p:
Chemical composition. Essential oil (thymol as the major component); phenolic acids (rosmarinic, ferulic, syringic, coumaric acids), tannins (gallic and protocatechuic acids), flavonoids (luteolin, apigenin, cirsilenol, thymonin, and derivatives, besides others) (
 Van Den Broucke and Lemli, 1983; 
 Kuete, 2017; 
 Salehi et al., 2019a).
